Animals
Dogs and cats are the most common household pets, while birds and fish are also popular companions. In the wild, lions roar to communicate, dogs bark to alert, and cats meow to express themselves.
Food
Pizza topped with cheese is a favorite fast food, while burgers are classic American cuisine. Pasta dishes like spaghetti are popular in Italian cooking. For dessert, ice cream and fresh apples make delicious treats.
Sports
Football and basketball are team sports played worldwide. Tennis requires precision and skill, while swimming and running are excellent individual exercises. Players kick the ball in football and shoot for goals in basketball.
